          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1619713277942-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the jam is done, transfer it to a bowl and leave to cool</p><p>Tip: The jam will thicken whilst it cools!</p><p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>beef mince</strong> and<strong> beef stock mix</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape into equal-sized patties (1 per person!) and put in the fridge until later</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619713302810-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
