          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1619713302810-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then separate your <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>and<strong> </strong>pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3-4 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Once done, set aside until serving (save the pan!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-1619713313564-x200.jpg",
